										<h1 class="pagetitle">For Marlin, Stripes Mean Stop</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">Drone footage reveals that marlin flash their bright stripes before going in for a kill.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
